'''Xylen chips''' were [[Droid/Legends|droid]] [[Memory chip/Legends|memory chips]] made from [[xylen]]. Their use was ended long before [[12 ABY/Legends|12 ABY]] due to the high cost of xylen. They were used in [[APD-40]] droids.

